text.tspan: Are the bolt-on shields more likely to be removed than the flip-up ones?
There is extremely strong evidence that bolt-on shields are more likely
to be removed than flip-up ones.
Employers are liable for workplace accidents. The power takeoff driveline on farm
tractors is covered by either a bolt-on or flip-up shiled, but both are often removed
on older tractors. The US National Safety Council sampled older tractors.
